Package: mutantr
Title: Mutation Testing for R Packages
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Fast mutation testing engine for R packages. Scans R source code
    for mutable operators (comparison, boolean, arithmetic, logical) and
    generates mutated variants to test against your test suite. Powered by a
    Rust backend via extendr for speed.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports:
    callr,
    cli,
    jsonlite
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Config/rextendr/version: 0.4.2
SystemRequirements: Cargo (Rust's package manager), rustc >= 1.65.0, xz
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.2)
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
